After CLimbing around in underground Casms for hours on end, The small group has finally Broke through to the Surface. A group of six. Spinner, Rock Tower, Chamelon, Chetar, Sure Shot and Starlight.
 
They begin looking in all directions till finnally Chetar picks up on Dracos Energy Signiture. And he picks up on a secondary signiture. The six decide to Take off in the Direction of the energy Signiture are Pointing.
